category: Devel
requires: cygwin libultragetopt0
external-source: ultragetopt
sdesc: "Versatile and customizable implementation of getopt (development)"
ldesc: "UltraGetopt is a versatile and customizable implementation of getopt()
with support for many common extensions, MS-DOS formatted option strings, and
much more.  It can function as a drop-in replacement for getopt() on systems
with or without existing vendor-provided implementations and also as a
separate co-existing function."
